ain from where you can see the peaks of Taurus mountains. Leaving the views of the cedar trees behind, a completely different vegetation cover will be waiting for us to offer lots of different surprises; nomads feeding their goats, wild horses&#8230;<br><\/p>\n<\/details>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>The minimum number of participants for the daily tours is 4.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>A. is easy \u2013 for anyone of any age.<br>B. is moderate \u2013 for anyone who is a \u201d\u02dcregular walker\u2019.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>The minimum number of participants for weekly tours is 2. The prices are per person and for pricing of bigger groups and for more information please contact our office.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons is-content-justification-center is-layout-flex wp-container-core-buttons-is-layout-3e41869c wp-block-buttons-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-button\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link wp-element-button\" href=\"https:\/\/dragoman-turkey.com\/i-want-to-join\/\">Join<\/a><\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Biking Tours<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-8eb45db6 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\" style=\"margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column has-border-color is-layout-flow wp-container-core-column-is-layout-a7dce961 wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"border-color:#e1e2e4;border-width:1px;border-radius:8px\">\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading is-service-name has-medium-font-size\" style=\"margin-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30);margin-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30);font-style:normal;font-weight:700\">Sar\u0131lar-Belenli<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns are-vertically-aligned-top is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-d743fdf5 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\" style=\"margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-top