ent and advanced climbing techniques: you just walk, climb, jump and swim and jump again! Along your path you will have the chance to explore the geological and ecological formations of this land, and you may observe marine birds, fish,crabs and sea turtles\u2026 Why not an elusive and very rare Mediterranean seal, if you are very lucky?<\/p>\n<\/details>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons is-content-justification-center is-layout-flex wp-container-core-buttons-is-layout-3e41869c wp-block-buttons-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-button\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link wp-element-button\" href=\"https:\/\/dragoman-turkey.com\/i-want-to-join\/\">Join<\/a><\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>The minimum number of the participants is 4. The prices are per person.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>The activity is suitable for 16-55 age group and requires the participants to have a good level of fitness.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Blue Cruises and Daily Boat Tours<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-8eb45db6 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\" style=\"margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column has-border-color is-layout-flow wp-container-core-column-is-layout-a7dce961 wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"border-color:#e1e2e4;border-width:1px;border-radius:8px\">\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading is-service-name has-medium-font-size\" style=\"margin-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30);margin-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30);font-style:normal;font-weight:700\">Ka\u015f Islands<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns are-vertically-aligned-top is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-d743fdf5 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\" style=\"margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-top is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\" style=\"margin-right:var(-